Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.14,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, in a crazy dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was gazin' up to the Promised Land
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:12.85,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らのユメの形　ザワメキ出す Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.86,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on let's go to that place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't stop anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:21.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛びだせ　仄暗い空　fly into the light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.49,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じたいこの世界に生まれたことが幸せってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:28.09,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代へ続く扉を開けるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:30.34,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.84,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なぁ、わかってるんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.77,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らはいつだって傷だらけで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.96,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲しみのルーツ断ち切って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怖くないよ　いつでも傍に感じるから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.36,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だから　もっと　もっと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.82,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱い　力が心満たしてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.89,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.27,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wake！ Up！ Your！ Heart！ Beat！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.56,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.41,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brave and boiling heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絆を示せ High！！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blazeに生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.35,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ドキドキ感じて Burning！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Over Boost！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:10.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a real deal！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.70,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more liars
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.93,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition's ON, my heart is on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fire Fire
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:19.30,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.34,0:01:06.14,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.45,0:01:08.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:12.85,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:14.86,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:16.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:21.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.91,0:01:25.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.49,0:01:28.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:30.34,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:33.84,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:36.77,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:38.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:42.67,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:45.36,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:49.82,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:54.27,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:57.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:59.56,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:04.06,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.35,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动  燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:09.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.70,0:02:10.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.93,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:16.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:19.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:35.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…and so, we met in the deep dark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.53,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come to us. They left us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:48.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We all abanded sadness. We all abanded kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.62,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The world is full of hatred. There's no hope, then take this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.31,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘で建った塔の　深層で燃える炎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.07,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（早々気を付けろ背後） 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.09,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A matter of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:03.25,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Be ready. Burn up！ Liars！ In this cold night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:06.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ただで消え去る罪など無い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:10.91,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh baby, cry out louder to this bad luck
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.71,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,God, hear the scream, share us your light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:22.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, now stand up and head up cause we're falling up
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.73,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,670)}（Who is the bloody liar？ You all the bloody liar）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.42,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創傷疼いている　何故痛いくらい 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:32.14,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah 今疼き出す…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.63,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:47.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's behind the truth. We know what we gotta do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.14,0:22:35.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们相遇在这个深幽破碎之境
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人会来 他们把我们留在这蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.25,0:22:48.72,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀遗弃了我们 仁慈遗弃了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.10,0:22:52.62,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界充满着憎恶 没有希望 执此前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:56.31,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用谎言树立的塔 在其深处燃烧的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.57,0:22:58.07,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（随时小心身后）
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.09,0:22:59.09,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太久
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:03.25,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好准备 燃烧吧骗子！在这冰冷的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:06.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赎罪必须付出代价
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:10.91,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢 宝贝 为你的厄运大声哭喊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.46,0:23:15.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 请聆听这哭号 赐下您的圣光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:22.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今夜 匍匐跌倒之人请起身抬头吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:18.73,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,50)}（谁是可恶的骗子？你们全是可恶的骗子）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.98,0:23:26.42,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创伤在隐隐作痛 为何如此痛彻心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:32.14,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 此刻疼痛再起...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.15,0:23:39.63,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.69,0:23:47.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是真相背后的故事 我们知道我们将做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是决定来拿走你们的手脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝美 为什么你在操纵炎帝？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用从宗也那借来的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.13,0:00:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能让炎帝误以为我是礼央子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事也能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想吃苦头的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就乖乖地任我宰割吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.32,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们也赢不了炎帝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.54,0:00:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可难说 现在的我们可不太一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.64,0:00:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？东
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.19,0:00:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看上去确实如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也是身负重任 绝不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.26,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:38.33,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\1c&HFFFFFF&}第十话 破碎的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样哪有机会抢到心脏...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没脸去见兄长大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.83,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到全都是些不中用的家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有必要惩罚你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个肮脏鼠辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们忘了我父亲对你们的救命之恩么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记他为一无所有的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供住处和热汤的恩情了么！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左脚和右脚竟敢反抗我这个心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你们总是嚣张过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...是啊是啊 你们要认清本分 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.24,0:03:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我来擦掉鼠辈们的脏血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想生来就当别人的脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,德尔苏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 去把他们的心脏抢来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我蒙羞了 我的妹妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.86,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.92,0:04:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行啊 东
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镰仓受的气就在这里还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热...好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是操控炎帝的感受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子大人 礼央子她...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都在忍受这种折磨么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把人看扁了 臭小鬼们！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 右手酱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行 现在的我们能够战胜炎帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是俄罗斯的舞武器使？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.19,0:05:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想让这两个女孩被烧死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你们拥有的舞武器全交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.70,0:05:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我交出所有舞武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是从父母那继承下来的宝贵舞武器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也无法替换你们的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的舞乱伎·桑帕萨一旦复活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必将会和炎帝一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 就让我在这里见识一下你那完全体的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝控制了他们的舞武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要攻过来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是夺回手脚的 完全体炎帝的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比佐 那个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 舞乱伎的力量还不止于此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把我所知道的心脏之秘密告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.79,0:07:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明王舞也变成了完全体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果炎帝还是更胜一筹么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不赶紧分出胜负的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身体就撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？那是美国的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是肥猪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏心脏 快破坏心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这种时候了他在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 就你多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要破坏心脏的话 舞乱伎的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 和笨蛋打交道真的很累
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个舞乱伎好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个大婶到底几公斤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦格尔拉 对丰满的女士提体重的事太失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非得帮他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘易斯 细节不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经与我以拳相交的东
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说与兄弟无异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 破坏掉心脏！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激发出舞乱伎真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏心脏？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 东 你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要听那个笨蛋的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是艾比佐冒着生命危险告诉我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个滥好人...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实也没其他招了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么大家一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预备...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.11,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧？心脏进入头颅了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞的脑袋内部吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.21,0:09:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 王舞漂浮在空中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定就是前往宝岛的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把拥有心脏的人类放入头颅作为大脑之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往舞乱伎巢穴的大门就会开启
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼央子说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 我不能让你们前往舞乱伎的巢穴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的一击...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是东干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.65,0:10:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝岛...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.92,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.17,0:10:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心脏进入头颅之时
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞乱伎会打开其故乡的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我好像忘了说一件重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:03.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}来自 薰子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 我来看看...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 破坏心脏进入头部之后会力量增强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二 宝岛的门会开启
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三 然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾比佐 这个不太妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 快点离开那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗也
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.41,0:11:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你的手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.94,0:11:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把我救上来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是把人类当作大脑的舞乱伎的真正样貌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体会到一些礼央子大人的觉悟了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人背负太多了啦 礼央子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能让她继续独自背负下去啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 比起跟礼央子大人同年的你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情反而是我这个小辈看得清
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你今年几岁了？36？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头才是 恭喜您跨上四整数大关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦耶！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就此告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有些私事要办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗也 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时 炎帝的心脏在王舞的攻击下与我分离
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在那一刻 舞乱伎就应该会停止活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却一直能感受到炎帝的呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎帝到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}来电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}医院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}固定电话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}稍后提醒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}文本回复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:18.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}音频讯息回复
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.76,0:13:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我了结恩怨的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是宝岛...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸一直想去的岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.32,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.86,0:14:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 回应一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞 想要把东吞掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.12,0:14:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王舞 谢谢你 一直保护着东
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然对你来说很必要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要把东带回去 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 东
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.11,0:15:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 你没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事是指 什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟东...你已经睡了整整三天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了三天？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白担心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 柊最担心你了 泪水都沾湿了枕头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 东
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的舞乱伎们都很安分的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...诶？是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是绝景呀 真是绝景呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.86,0:16:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来到这里是有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座岛是不可思议的集合体    
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来 生物们是不可能在这座岛上繁衍生息的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是有什么神秘力量在维持这座岛的生态体系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想说的不是这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一家人刚来到这座岛时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要猎鸟抓鱼来吃的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这座岛似乎大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我们吃土豆它都很惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整天这样我们也很困扰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你们不用在意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.76,0:17:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭 要多吃一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汀小姐 我想接着说刚才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想请你...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汀小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是柊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过柊也变了很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.30,0:18:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想请汀小姐...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.53,0:18:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想请汀小姐回到地面 和我们一起对抗礼央子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这就是你的目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要离开地面 舍弃老爸来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想问她原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是忙忙农活干干杂务之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都变得无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你的优点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.75,0:18:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？你是指什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什么呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 木乃亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个叫新走的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是...做过...了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么！可能嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.24,0:19:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是 亲嘴...是亲过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这什么蠢问题啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲是亲过了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金酱 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.12,0:19:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是 您也晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝岛明明在很高的地方 却一点不冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.83,0:20:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨她说还是要留在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.04,0:20:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我说 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢这里 很喜欢宝岛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里有种非常亲切的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是东酱的故乡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想爸爸他一定也会很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东酱 谢谢你带我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够回到这里也是因为那天我遇到了黄金酱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要说 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下 我的舞乱伎·桑帕萨就能复苏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好无聊 太不经打了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.56,0:21:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的无首们 好像处于半睡半醒之中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能落后于其他舞乱伎队伍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也去夺取心脏 艾比佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷走睡着的舞乱伎们的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种卑鄙的手段...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞口水！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这个声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看森林
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个地方比想象中要好得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.23,0:21:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为是个地狱般的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新走？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙是怎么来到这里的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们打开了这里的门
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是跟着你们进来罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.44,0:22:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来其他国家的人也来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得像祭典一样热闹了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 有趣至极的舞乱伎狩猎开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
